    {
      "id": "19374a43-3c04-4533-9b37-8c3e20b35ec3",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $\\alpha\\ge 1$ on a par convexité~:\n             $2^{1-\\alpha}(i+j)^\\alpha \\le i^\\alpha+j^\\alpha \\le (i+j)^\\alpha$\n             donc il y a convergence ssi $\\alpha > 2$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha\\ge 1\\)</span> on a par\nconvexité : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2^{1-\\alpha}(i+j)^\\alpha \\le\ni^\\alpha+j^\\alpha \\le (i+j)^\\alpha\\)</span> donc il y a convergence ssi\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha &gt; 2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
